{"record_id":"kheirkhah-2025_P11_peak_01","source_id":"kheirkhah-2025","source_class":"clinical_lit","reuse_status":"permitted","participant_id":"P11","n_in_source":43,"context":{"clinical":true,"route":"IV","dose_tier":"moderate","infusion_profile":"single","setting":{"music":true,"eye_mask":true,"therapist_present":true,"alone":false}},"reported_phase":"peak","phase_inference_basis":"Within-session oscillation between fear and beauty at peak.","subjective_dimensions":{"dissociation":0.5,"body_detachment":0.25,"time_distortion":0.25,"emotional_valence":0.25,"fear":0.75,"loss_of_agency":0.5,"meaningfulness":0.5},"narrative_features":{"identity_shift":false,"death_rebirth_theme":false,"cosmic_scale":false,"medical_anxiety":true,"childhood_memory":false,"entity_or_presence":false,"floating_or_falling":false,"tunnel_void_space_imagery":false},"raw_excerpt":"I felt my heart racing through some of it, especially when I started freaking out, wondering if I was going to have an anxiety attack during the experience … When I was able to get on top of my thoughts though, it was really beautiful … It was mostly going great even when my anxiety would kick in over the 'high' I felt.","raw_excerpt_completeness":"full","source_theme_label":"Different Levels of Depression and Anxiety — Heightened anxiety","notes":"Within-peak oscillation. medical_anxiety=true (heart racing, fear of anxiety attack). Despite high fear, valence net positive — top-of-thoughts state-switching.","annotator_id":"claude-opus-4-7-2026-04-24","annotated_at":"2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}
